<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #130E06;
        }
    </style>

</head>
<body>
<div className="email-body">
    <h1>Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video "<%= title %>"</p>
    <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
    <p>Thank you for being part of our community!</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>